# Claude Token Saver (`claude_interaction_tool`)

This repository is **Claude Token Saver** (GitHub: Claude-Token-Saver). It is a **different product** from any separate **GitHub App Installer** work — do not merge naming or assume they are the same app.

**PyInstaller output:** `dist/ClaudeTokenSaver/ClaudeTokenSaver.exe`

**After `py -3 build_exe.py`:** a full copy of the build folder is also written to **`Desktop/ClaudeTokenSaver/`** (Windows).

**To open the exe:** `scripts/open_token_saver_exe.ps1` or `.cmd`, or run either path above. If missing, `py -3 build_exe.py` from repo root.

**Dev (no build):** `py -3 -m claude_backend.gui`
